history.content:
The annual Berkeley Data Science Forum for this semester is back! On 4/28, Data Science Society at Berkeley will be hosting its 3rd Annual Data Science Forum. Our theme for this year covers a topic that is trending among many people, both within and outside of industry: Artificial Intelligence.
We will bring you 8 leading industry figures from companies like Spotify, McKinsey & Company, Cisco, Nvidia, Amazon, Yelp, Atheer, and Pinterest! These speakers will share their research, insights, and findings. Come for a chance to learn from industry leaders, network with professionals, and to share your resume!
Check out more at https://www.eventbrite.com/e/berkeley-data-science-forum-2018-tickets-45218929034
history.subject: Berkeley Data Science Forum on 4/28
